야","body":"……마스키, 뭔가 좋은 일 있었지?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"맞아.\n실은, 마야 씨가 신곡을 엄청 칭찬해 줬거든!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"파레오","body":"파스파레의 마야 씨가!?\n맛스 씨, 마야 씨를 만나셨나요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":34,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"응, 요전 연습 후에 우연히.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}]