마스킹","body":"하핫, 츄츄라면 그렇게 말할 줄 알았어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"……마야 씨의 감상을 들으니까, 왠지 말이지……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"드러머로서 내가 칭찬받았을 때도 기쁘지만,\nRAS가 칭찬받았을 때가\n몇 배나 더 기쁘다고 느꼈어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"그 마음, 저도 알 것 같아요..\n우리의 노래와 연주를 누구보다도 좋아하니까\n그걸 알아주는 것이 기쁘다고 할까요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"그래, 그거야!\nRAS 굉장하지! 라며 좀 더 자랑하고 싶어지는 느낌!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"기분이 확~ 들떠서 왠지 가만히 있을 수가 없었거든……\n정신 차리고 보니까 바이크로 질주했더라고.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"록","body":"그럴 때 여행을 떠나면 기분 좋을 것 같네요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"진~짜 기분 좋았어!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"fes2-MK-part2-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"쓸데없는 생각 안 하고, 머리 